platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Don’t be fooled by the cute visuals and quirky dialogue. Beneath the charming sheen, Warbits is a deceptively complex strategy game. As you make your way through a campaign packed with turn-based battles, you’re forced to make tough decisions. Do you try to stealthily capture an enemy base or wage a full-on assault and put your strongest units at risk? With a challenging campaign and several multiplayer game types (including a same-screen local mode!), your tactics will be put to the test.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Devise complex strategies to come out on top.
Stratèges en herbe ou confirmés, vous allez vous régaler.
